spec_data.Name: python-XStatic-Hogan
spec_data.Description:
Hogan JavaScript library packaged for setuptools
(easy_install) / pip.

This package is intended to be used by **any** project
that needs these files.

It intentionally does **not** provide any extra code
except some metadata
**nor** has any extra requirements. You MAY use some
minimal support code from
the XStatic base package, if you like.
